OL,3,C'It affects your whole life': Calls to
OL,4,Cchange perceptions of tinnitus:
OL,6,FTinnitus can have a grave impact on
OL,7,Fthe mental health of those who suffer,
OL,8,Fwith 1 in 5 experiencing thoughts of
OL,9,Fsuicide or self-harm in the last year.
OL,11,FEmyr Williams, who lives in Nercwys in
OL,12,FFlintshire, spoke about the day-to-day
OL,13,Feffects of tinnitus. He said: "It's a
OL,14,Fcondition that affects your whole
OL,15,Flife, there is an awful sound in the
OL,16,Fbackground all of the time.
