OL,3,C'It affects your whole life': Calls to
OL,4,Cchange perceptions of tinnitus:
OL,6,F"One of the most important things is
OL,7,Fto raise awareness that those who live
OL,8,Fwith tinnitus will not necessarily
OL,9,Fhave any clear indication, such as a
OL,10,Fhearing aid, to show that they do."
OL,12,FRaising awareness
OL,14,FA Cardiff-based audiologist has raised
OL,15,Fconcerns over how tinnitus is
OL,16,Fperceived within the public and health
OL,17,Fprofessions.
