OL,3,C'It affects your whole life': Calls to
OL,4,Cchange perceptions of tinnitus:
OL,6,F, says "more must be done" to ensure
OL,7,Fthat those affected by tinnitus
OL,8,Freceive "bespoke treatment" to help
OL,9,Fthem navigate the difficulties of life
OL,10,Fwith the condition.
OL,12,FMs Jones also noted that it is "very
OL,13,Foften" the case where health
OL,14,Fprofessionals say that nothing can be
OL,15,Fdone about the condition.
OL,17,F"It's really important that we can
OL,18,Fensure that health professionals have
OL,19,Fappropriate training and are very
OL,20,Fhappy to reach out to the likes of
OL,21,Faudiologists to learn more."
