OL,3,C'It affects your whole life': Calls to
OL,4,Cchange perceptions of tinnitus:
OL,6,FAs someone who has been diagnosed with
OL,7,Fthe condition, Ms Jones urged those
OL,8,Fwho believe they are suffering as a
OL,9,Fresult of tinnitus to contact their GP
OL,10,Fand access the resources available on
OL,11,Fthe Tinnitus UK website.
